   "## Common pitfalls\n",
   "\n",
   "- Infinite loops when tool always errors and model retries forever \u2014 mitigated by `max_turns`.\n",
   "- Mutating the system prompt mid-turn (breaks caching and reproducibility).\n",
   "- Not persisting tool messages to the session store.\n"
  ]
 },
